message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this incredible product. I think you'll really love it. Would you like to make an offer on it?
Thank you for offering me the product, Alice. I appreciate your enthusiasm. I would like to make a counteroffer of $9500.
I appreciate your interest in the product, Bob. However, I was thinking more along the lines of $11500. Would you be willing to meet me at that price?
I understand your position, Alice. Considering my budget constraints, I would like to propose a counteroffer of $10000.
